name: Sega Ages: Memorial Selection Vol. 2
overview: Sega Ages Memorial Selection Vol.2 (SEGA AGES メモリアルセレクションVOL.2) is a compilation of six 1980s arcade games and released for the Sega Saturn in 1997 only in Japan. - Doki Doki Penguin Land - Samurai - Sindbad Mystery - Star Jacker - Monaco GP - Ninja Princess
